description: This file defines a React functional component named CouponEditPage, which uses React Router's useParams hook to determine whether to display a 'Create Coupon' or 'Edit Coupon' heading based on the URL parameter 'id'. It renders a simple UI structure with a header and a placeholder paragraph.

methods.name: CouponEditPage()
methods.description: React functional component that renders a coupon creation or editing page based on URL parameters.
